:0:{}}}'),(12247,23704,'_wp_attachment_image_alt','Phone-Support-Case-Study-Central-Freight-Lines'),(12248,23698,'content_page_3_options','Case Study'),(12249,23698,'_content_page_3_options','field_636abf0c122fe'),(12250,23698,'content_page_3_case_study_background_image','23603'),(12251,23698,'_content_page_3_case_study_background_image','field_636ad9ba2c841'),(12252,23698,'content_page_3_case_study_title','Case Study: Central Freight Lines'),(12253,23698,'_content_page_3_case_study_title','field_636ac29a5fac0'),(12254,23698,'content_page_3_case_study_image','23704'),(12255,23698,'_content_page_3_case_study_image','field_636ac2a35fac1'),(12256,23698,'content_page_3_case_study_content','When Avaya told Central Freight Lines that their telecom infrastructure consisting of over 20 legacy Avaya PBX systems was â€œEnd of Lifeâ€ and â€œEnd of Supportâ€ there were concerns that they wouldnâ€™t be able to get the maintenance support they needed. Central Freight Lines had a five year plan to convert all of their legacy PBX systems to cloud based phone systems so purchasing expensive upgrades for all their sites simply wasnâ€™t an option. Because Morgan BirgÃ© doesnâ€™t sunset legacy equipment and force our customers into unwanted upgrades and because we create maintenance agreements and contracts that fit our customers needs we were a perfect service partner for Central Freight Lines.'),(12257,23698,'_content_page_3_case_study_content','field_636ac2ab5fac2'),(12258,23698,'content_page_3_case_study_list_0_content','<h3>We Assessed</h3>\r\nAfter meeting with Central Freight Linesâ€™ IT staff and analyzing and inventorying their Avaya infrastructure we created a maintenance plan that provided world class support coupled with features like onsite crash kits, free helpdesk and carrier support, that surpassed what they received from Avaya. Our service plan also and provided them with the flexibility their CFO needed as we allowed them to take their locations off maintenance coverage without penalty when they were ready to convert to the cloud based phone system.'),(12259,23698,'_content_page_3_case_study_list_0_content','field_636ac2fa5fac4'),(12260,23698,'content_page_3_case_study_list_1_content','<h3>We Deployed</h3>\r\nProactive support is what separates us from our competition. As soon as our contract with Central Freight Lines started we dispatched a technician to all of their locations in order to check their system for errors and alarms, setup remote monitoring, obtain disaster recovery backup files and install a new UPS battery backup unit. Doing the little things at the beginning and visiting each site helped clear up system issues that we inherited from the previous vendor and made sure that all the phone systems were stable going forward. After our initial visits we sent crash kits with essential spare parts to all their locations for use in an emergency.'),(12261,23698,'_content_page_3_case_study_list_1_content','field_636ac2fa5fac4'),(12262,23698,'content_page_3_case_study_list_2_content','<h3>We Supported</h3>\r\nFor the last 6 years we have provided Central Freight lines with excellent support. Our helpdesk has worked hand in hand with their IT department to ensure voice communication between their freight terminals is always working and crash kits with spare parts ensures that if there is an outage we can recover quickly. In addition to providing excellent support for their legacy systems we also have assisted their IT staff with the transition to their cloud based phone systems, ensuring that their new technology is properly configured to support all of their locations.'),(12263,23698,'_content_page_3_case_study_list_2_content','field_636ac2fa5fac4'),(12264,23698,'content_page_3_case_study_list','3'),(12265,23698,'_content_page_3_case_study_list','field_636ac2d45fac3'),(12266,23698,'content_page_3_case_study',''),(12267,23698,'_content_page_3_case_study','field_636ac2825fabf'),(12268,23705,'content_page_0_options','Content S